-- Hartford Forecasts Fourth-Quarter EPS of 87 Cents to 92 Cents
-- B y   M a r c i   J a c o b s
-- 2013-10-29T13:03:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-29/hartford-forecasts-fourth-quarter-eps-of-87-cents-to-92-cents.html
Hartford Financial Services Group
Inc., the insurer shifting its focus to property-casualty
coverage, said it expects operating earnings per share of 87
cents to 92 cents this quarter.  Core earnings in the period will be $420 million to $445
million, according to a presentation posted today on the website
of Hartford, which is based in the Connecticut city of the same
name.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marci Jacobs in  New York  at 
